---item_49 Infused Pulsar---
Type :: Gun
Slot :: Gun
Gun Definition :: [[Infused Pulsar]]
Rarity :: Exotic

Bullets from this weapon can pierce multiple targets. 
When bullets make contact with an enemy, spawn a damage over time "Infused Pulsar Pool" at the enemy's position for 3 seconds.

Surprise, bet you didn't expect that!

